crosoft-learn\"></a> Microsoft Learn</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/contribute/content/markdown-reference\">Markdown reference for Microsoft Learn - Contributor guide | Microsoft Learn</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Microsoft Learn 还支持自定义 Markdown 扩展。</p>\n<p>例如：警报（备注、提示、重要提示、提醒、警告）</p>\n\n<div class=\"callout\" data-callout=\"note\">\n<div class=\"callout-title\">\n<div class=\"callout-title-icon\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-pencil\"><path d=\"M17 3a2.85 2.83 0 1 1 4 4L7.5 20.5 2 22l1.5-5.5Z\"/><path d=\"m15 5 4 4\"/></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Note</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-content\"><p>Information the user should notice even if skimming.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"callout\" data-callout=\"tip\">\n<div class=\"callout-title\">\n<div class=\"callout-title-icon\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flame\"><path d=\"M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z\"/></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Tip</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-content\"><p>Optional information to help a user be more successful.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"callout\" data-callout=\"important\">\n<div class=\"callout-title\">\n<div class=\"callout-title-icon\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flame\"><path d=\"M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z\"/></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Important</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-content\"><p>Essential information required for user success.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"callout\" data-callout=\"caution\">\n<div class=\"callout-title\">\n<div class=\"callout-title-icon\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-alert-triangle\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z\"/><path d=\"M12 9v4\"/><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"/></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Caution</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-content\"><p>Negative potential consequences of an action.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"callout\" data-callout=\"warning\">\n<div class=\"callout-title\">\n<div class=\"callout-title-icon\">\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-alert-triangle\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z\"/><path d=\"M12 9v4\"/><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"/></svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-title-inner\">Warning</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-content\"><p>Dangerous certain consequences of an action.</p>\n</div></div><p>其他语法详见文档：<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/contribute/markdown-reference\">Microsoft Learn 的 Markdown 参考 - Contributor guide | Microsoft Learn</a></p>\n","raw":"---\ntitle: Callouts 样式测试\ntags:\n  - Callouts\n  - GFM\n  - OFM\ncover: 'https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202604161933511.webp'\ncover_ref:\n  - null\ndescription: 又又又分离出一篇文章\nkatex: false\nassistant_model:\n  - null\ncategories:\n  - 阿-测试文章\nabbrlink: d4d78bd0\nsummary: >-\n  本文介绍了 Callouts 样式的测试方法，包括不同类型的 Callouts 及其展示效果。文章首先列出了 Obsidian 中支持的 Callouts\n  类型，如 note、abstract、summary 等，并提供了示例内容。接着，文章展示了如何在不打断笔记流的情况下使用标注附加内容，以及如何折叠和展开\n  Callouts。此外，文章还提到了 GFM 中的 Callouts 样式，并给出了 Microsoft Learn 中自定义 Markdown\n  扩展的示例。最后，文章强调了参考相关文档的重要性，以便更好地理解和应用这些样式。\ndate: 2023-06-01 22:06:06\ncover_prompt:\ncover_model:\ntop_img:\n---\n\n> [!info] 本文于 `260416` 解耦自 [[Markdown 渲染测试]]。\n\n本文将测试各种 Callouts 块的展示效果。\n\n# Obsidian\n\n支持以下类型：\n\n- note\n- abstract, summary, tldr\n- info\n- todo\n- tip, hint, important\n- success, check, done\n- question, help, faq\n- warning, caution, attention\n- failure, fail, missing\n- danger, error\n- bug\n- example\n- quote, cite\n\n> [!Any]\n> 当类型不在列表中时。\n\n> [!note]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!abstract]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!summary]\n\n> [!tldr]\n\n> [!info]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!todo]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!tip]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!hint]\n\n> [!important]\n\n> [!success]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!check]\n\n> [!done]\n\n> [!question]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!help]\n\n> [!faq]\n\n> [!warning]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!caution]\n\n> [!attention]\n\n> [!failure]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!fail]\n\n> [!missing]\n\n> [!danger]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!error]\n\n> [!bug]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!example]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!quote]\n> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\n\n> [!cite]\n\n折叠：\n\n> [!question]- 折叠尝试（无折叠内容）\n\n> [!cite]- 折叠尝试（默认关）\n> 折叠内容\n\n> [!success]+ 折叠尝试（默认开）\n> 折叠内容\n\n在不打断笔记流的情况下使用标注附加内容。\n\n> [!info]\n> 默认标题\n> Here's a callout block.\n> It supports **Markdown**, *Wikilinks and embeds*!\n>\n> 无序列表：\n>\n> - 项目 1\n>\n> 有序列表：\n>\n> 1. 项目 a\n\n> [!tip] 自定义标题\n> 公式渲染：\n>\n> $$\n> r+v-e=2\n> $$\n>\n> 行内代码：`Class<?> class = MyClass.class;`\n>\n> 图片：![图片链接](https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202604161940024.webp)\n\n> [!error] 标题内公式 $a^2+b^2=c^2$，标题内代码 `Hello world!`\n\n> [!cite] 标题内图片：![图片链接](https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202604161940024.webp)图片后文字\n\n> [!question] Can callouts be nested?\n> > [!todo] Yes!, they can.\n> > > [!example]+  You can even use multiple layers of nesting.\n> > > > [!cite]- 折叠尝试\n> > > > 折叠内容\n\n参考：[Callouts](https://help.obsidian.md/Editing+and+formatting/Callouts)\n\n# GFM\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> Keep this in mind.\n\n> [!TIP]\n> Here's a suggestion.\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> Be careful.\n\n> [!CAUTION]\n> Be extremely careful.\n\n参考：[Style guide - GitHub Docs](https://docs.github.com/en/contributing/style-guide-and-content-model/style-guide)\n\n# Microsoft Learn\n\n> 参考：[Markdown reference for Microsoft Learn - Contributor guide | Microsoft Learn](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/contribute/content/markdown-reference)\n\nMicrosoft Learn 还支持自定义 Markdown 扩展。\n\n例如：警报（备注、提示、重要提示、提醒、警告）\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> Information the user should notice even if skimming.\n\n> [!TIP]\n> Optional information to help a user be more successful.\n\n> [!IMPORTANT]\n> Essential information required for user success.\n\n> [!CAUTION]\n> Negative potential consequences of an action.\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> Dangerous certain consequences of an action.\n\n其他语法详见文档：[Microsoft Learn 的 Markdown 参考 - Contributor guide | Microsoft Learn](https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/contribute/markdown-reference)","categories":[{"name":"阿-测试文章","api":"api/categories/阿-测试文章.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Callouts","api":"api/tags/Callouts.json"},{"name":"GFM","api":"api/tags/GFM.json"},{"name":"OFM","api":"api/tags/OFM.json"}]},"api":"api/posts/p/d4d78bd0.json"}